{
  "name": "HoloScript Development",
  "description": "HoloScript language with HoloScript MCP (this repo) and Brittney MCP (Hololand repo) - both usable by Brittney or cloud agents",
  
  "mcpServers": {
    "holoscript": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["tsx", "packages/mcp-server/src/index.ts"],
      "cwd": "${workspaceFolder}"
    },
    "hololand": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["tsx", "../Hololand/packages/brittney/mcp-server/src/index.ts"],
      "cwd": "${workspaceFolder}",
      "env": {
        "HOLOLAND_API_URL": "http://localhost:3000",
        "BRITTNEY_SERVICE_URL": "http://localhost:11435",
        "BRITTNEY_ADMIN_KEY": "mcp-localhost-trusted"
      }
    }
  },

  "instructions": [
    "You are working in the HoloScript language repository.",
    "",
    "## ALWAYS Use MCP Tools for HoloScript",
    "",
    "Before writing or editing HoloScript code, use these tools:",
    "- `parse_hs` - Parse .hs/.hsplus files",
    "- `parse_holo` - Parse .holo compositions",
    "- `validate_holoscript` - Check for errors",
    "",
    "For code generation:",
    "- `generate_object` - Create objects from descriptions",
    "- `generate_scene` - Create complete compositions",
    "- `suggest_traits` - Get appropriate VR traits",
    "",
    "For trait information:",
    "- `list_traits` - See all 49 VR traits",
    "- `explain_trait` - Get detailed trait documentation",
    "",
    "For documentation:",
    "- `get_syntax_reference` - Syntax help",
    "- `get_examples` - Code examples",
    "- `explain_code` - Plain English explanation",
    "",
    "## HoloScript File Formats",
    "",
    "| Extension | Purpose | Parser |",
    "|-----------|---------|--------|",
    "| `.hs` | Classic object-centric | `parse_hs` |",
    "| `.hsplus` | With VR traits | `parse_hs` |",
    "| `.holo` | Compositions | `parse_holo` |",
    "",
    "## Package Structure",
    "",
    "- `@holoscript/core` - Parser and AST",
    "- `@holoscript/traits` - 49 VR trait definitions",
    "- `@holoscript/compiler` - Multi-target compilation",
    "- `@holoscript/mcp-server` - MCP tools for AI agents",
    "",
    "## Use Brittney for Runtime Help",
    "",
    "The Hololand MCP server provides Brittney AI tools:",
    "- `brittney_explain_scene` - Understand running scenes",
    "- `brittney_suggest_fix` - Get fix suggestions",
    "- `brittney_auto_fix` - Auto-fix browser errors"
  ],

  "contextFiles": [
    ".github/copilot-instructions.md",
    "docs/MCP_SERVER_GUIDE.md",
    "docs/MCP_CONFIGURATION.md"
  ],

  "preferredTools": [
    "parse_hs",
    "parse_holo",
    "validate_holoscript",
    "generate_object",
    "generate_scene",
    "suggest_traits",
    "list_traits",
    "explain_trait",
    "get_syntax_reference"
  ]
}
